─── DESIGN DIRECTION ────────────────────────────────────────

Theme: Modern Safety Green + White
  Professional, clean, practical for daily EHS operations
  Not corporate-boring. Not flashy startup.
  Think: a tool field officers actually enjoy using.

─── CSS DESIGN TOKENS ───────────────────────────────────────

Locate the global CSS file (globals.css / index.css / 
app.css / variables.css — whichever exists).
Add or replace CSS custom properties in :root.

DO NOT remove any existing variables that are used elsewhere.
ADD new ones and REPLACE color values where safe:

:root {

  /* ── BACKGROUNDS ── */
  --bg-base:          #F5FAF6;   /* page canvas, soft green-white */
  --bg-surface:       #FFFFFF;   /* cards, panels */
  --bg-sunken:        #EEF4EF;   /* input fills, code areas */
  --bg-sidebar:       #0F2318;   /* deep forest sidebar */
  --bg-overlay:       #FFFFFF;   /* modals, dropdowns */

  /* ── BORDERS ── */
  --border-subtle:    #D9E9DA;
  --border-default:   #B8D4BA;
  --border-strong:    #7BAE7F;

