─── TABLE: ObservationTable.jsx ─────────────────────────────

Build a complete, responsive table component.

COLUMNS (in order):
  1.  # / ID (observation_id)
  2.  Date + Day (combined: "15 Mar\nMonday")
  3.  Time
  4.  Title (max 200px, truncate with tooltip)
  5.  Reported By
  6.  Team
  7.  Category
  8.  Priority (PriorityBadge)
  9.  Status (StatusBadge + quick-change dropdown)
  10. Responsible Person
  11. Target Date (red text if overdue)
  12. Actions (View / Edit / Delete icons)

TABLE STYLING:
  Container:
    background: var(--bg-surface)
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle)
    border-radius: var(--radius-md)
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm)
    overflow: hidden
    margin-top: 0

  Header row:
    background: var(--bg-sunken)
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-subtle)
    th: 11px, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.06em, 
        weight 600, var(--text-tertiary)
        padding: 11px 14px

  Body rows:
    td: 13px, var(--text-primary), padding: 13px 14px
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle)
    transition: background var(--transition-fast)
    hover: background var(--bg-sunken)

  OVERDUE ROW HIGHLIGHT:
    When status === 'Overdue':
      background: rgba(239,68,68,0.04)
      border-left: 3px solid var(--danger-500)
    The Target Date cell: color var(--danger-600), weight 600

  Quick status update:
    Status cell contains StatusBadge.
    On click: show small inline dropdown with status options.
    On select: call updateStatus(id, { status: newStatus })
    Show brief loading state during API call.

  Empty state (no records):
    Centered content, padding 60px 0
    Icon: 48px, var(--text-tertiary)
    "No observations found" — 15px, weight 600
    "Try adjusting your filters" — 13px, var(--text-tertiary)
    "Add Observation" button below

  Loading skeleton: show 5 skeleton rows while loading

  Mobile behavior (<768px):
    Hide columns: Time, Manager, Responsible Person
    Make table horizontally scrollable inside wrapper
    wrapper: overflow-x: auto, -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch

  Pagination:
    Below table, border-top: 1px var(--border-subtle)
    padding: 14px 16px
    "Showing X–Y of Z results" left
    Previous/Next + page numbers right
    Active page: var(--green-600) bg, white

