  Entry animation: translateX(100%) → translateX(0)
                   260ms ease-out
  Exit: reverse, 180ms ease-in

DRAWER HEADER:
  "Add Observation" or "Edit Observation" (h2)
  Close button (×) top-right
  border-bottom: 1px var(--border-subtle)
  padding: 20px 24px

FORM SECTIONS:

  Section 1 — Identification (auto-generated, read-only):
    Observation ID: [OBS-2026-XXXX] — auto, greyed input
    Date + Time: side by side (required)
    Day: auto-calculated from date, readonly

  Section 2 — Observation Details:
    Title (required, full-width)
    Description (required, textarea min-height 100px)
    Category (select dropdown)
    Priority (select: Low/Medium/High/Critical)

  Section 3 — People:
    Reported By (required)
    Responsible Team
    Supervisor Name
    Manager Name
    Responsible / Concerned Person

  Section 4 — Status & Dates:
    Status (select)
    Target Completion Date 
      (required when status = Open or In Progress)
    Actual Closure Date 
      (required when status = Closed)
    Corrective Measures 
      (textarea, required when status = Closed)
    Remarks (textarea, optional)
    Verified By (optional)

  Section 5 — Photos:
    Before Rectification Photo (file input)
      Accept: image/*, max 5MB
      Show preview thumbnail after selection
    After Rectification Photo (file input)
      Same as above

FORM VALIDATION (client-side, before API call):
  Show inline error below each invalid field
  
  Rules:
    title: required, min 3 chars
    description: required, min 10 chars
    observed_date: required
    observed_time: required
    reported_by: required
    target_completion_date: required if status is 
      'Open' or 'In Progress'
    actual_closure_date: required if status is 'Closed'
    corrective_measures: required if status is 'Closed'

FORM FOOTER:
  border-top: 1px var(--border-subtle)
  padding: 16px 24px
  right-aligned: [Cancel] [Save Observation]
  Loading state on Save button during API call

─── DETAIL VIEW: ObservationDetail.jsx ──────────────────────

Full-width drawer or modal showing complete observation.

SECTIONS:

  Header:
    Observation ID + StatusBadge + PriorityBadge
    Title (large, bold)
    "Observed on [Date] [Day] at [Time]" (secondary text)
    Edit button (if user has permission)

  Grid section (2-column on desktop, 1 on mobile):
    Reported By | Team Name
    Supervisor | Manager
    Responsible Person | Category
    Target Date | Closure Date
    Verified By | Last Updated

  Description:
    Full description text, proper line-height

  Corrective Measures:
    Shown only if filled. Label + full text.

  Remarks:
    Shown only if filled.

  Photos section:
    Before and After photos side by side
    Thumbnails: 200px × 150px, object-cover, radius md
    Click to open full-size (lightbox or new tab)
    Label above each: "Before Rectification" / 
                      "After Rectification"
    Show "No photo" placeholder if empty

  Audit Trail:
    "Created by [name] on [date]"
    "Last updated by [name] on [date]"
    Small, var(--text-tertiary), bottom of detail

─── CHARTS: ObservationCharts.jsx ───────────────────────────

Use the existing chart library (check inspection findings).
If Recharts: use Recharts components
If Chart.js: use react-chartjs-2
If ApexCharts: use apexcharts
If none installed: use Recharts 
  (add to package.json: npm install recharts)

Build an analytics section with TABS:
  Tab 1: Overview
  Tab 2: By Category & Priority  
  Tab 3: By Team & Officer

TAB 1 — Overview:
  Row 1 (2 charts side by side):
    Chart A: Monthly Observation Trend (Line chart)
      X-axis: months, Y-axis: count
      Lines: Total (green) / Open (blue) / Closed (grey)
      
    Chart B: Status Distribution (Donut chart)
      Segments: Open/In Progress/Closed/Overdue
      Colors: match status colors

  Row 2 (1 chart full-width):
    Chart C: Weekly Observations (Bar chart)
      Last 12 weeks
      Bars: green for closed, red for overdue

TAB 2 — By Category:
  Chart D: Observations by Category (Horizontal bar)
    Bars colored with --green-500
    Sorted by count descending

  Chart E: Priority Distribution (Bar chart)
    Low/Medium/High/Critical with semantic colors

TAB 3 — By Team:
  Chart F: Observations by Team (Bar chart)
    --green-600 bars

  Chart G: Top 10 Safety Officers by submissions (Bar)
    Horizontal, ranked

CHART STYLING:
  All charts:
    background: var(--bg-surface)
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle)
    border-radius: var(--radius-md)
    padding: 20px 16px
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm)

  All text: var(--text-secondary), var(--font-sans), 13px
  Grid lines: var(--border-subtle)
  Animation: CSS fadeIn 0.4s 0.2s both (chart-container class)

─── MAIN PAGE: ObservationPage.jsx ──────────────────────────

Extend the EXISTING Observation page file.
Replace the current content (keep routing and imports).

Structure:

import { useState } from 'react';
import { useObservations } from './hooks/useObservations';
import { ObservationKPICards } from './components/ObservationKPICards';
import { ObservationFilters } from './components/ObservationFilters';
import { ObservationTable } from './components/ObservationTable';
import { ObservationForm } from './components/ObservationForm';
import { ObservationDetail } from './components/ObservationDetail';
import { ObservationCharts } from './components/ObservationCharts';

export default function ObservationPage() {
    const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState('list'); 
    // 'list' | 'analytics'
    const [showForm, setShowForm] = useState(false);
    const [editingObs, setEditingObs] = useState(null);
    const [viewingObs, setViewingObs] = useState(null);

    const {
        observations, stats, loading, statsLoading,
        error, pagination, filters, setFilters,
        createObservation, updateObservation,
        updateStatus, deleteObservation, exportCSV,
        refresh,
    } = useObservations();

    const handleAddNew = () => {
        setEditingObs(null);
        setShowForm(true);
    };

    const handleEdit = (obs) => {
        setEditingObs(obs);
        setShowForm(true);
    };

    const handleView = (obs) => {
        setViewingObs(obs);
    };

    const handleFormSubmit = async (formData) => {
        if (editingObs) {
            await updateObservation(editingObs.id, formData);
        } else {
            await createObservation(formData);
        }
        setShowForm(false);
        setEditingObs(null);
    };

    return (
        <div className="obs-page">
            
            {/* PAGE HEADER */}
            <div className="obs-page__header">
                <div>
                    <h1 className="obs-page__title">
                        Daily EHS Observations
                    </h1>
                    <p className="obs-page__subtitle">
                        Track, manage, and close site safety 
                        observations
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div className="obs-page__actions">
                    <button 
                        className="btn btn-secondary"
                        onClick={() => exportCSV()}
                    >
                        Export CSV
                    </button>
                    <button 
                        className="btn btn-primary"
                        onClick={handleAddNew}
                    >
                        + Add Observation
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            {/* KPI CARDS */}
            <ObservationKPICards 
                kpis={stats?.kpis} 
                loading={statsLoading} 
            />

            {/* TAB NAVIGATION */}
            <div className="obs-tabs">
                <button 
                    className={`obs-tab ${
                        activeTab === 'list' ? 'active' : ''
                    }`}
                    onClick={() => setActiveTab('list')}
                >
                    Observation List
                </button>
                <button 
                    className={`obs-tab ${
                        activeTab === 'analytics' ? 'active' : ''
                    }`}
                    onClick={() => setActiveTab('analytics')}
                >
                    Analytics & Charts
                </button>
            </div>

            {/* TAB CONTENT */}
            {activeTab === 'list' && (
                <>
                    <ObservationFilters
                        filters={filters}
                        onFilterChange={(key, val) => 
                            setFilters(prev => ({
                                ...prev, 
                                [key]: val, 
                                page: 1,
                            }))
                        }
                        onExport={exportCSV}
                        loading={loading}
                    />
                    {error && (
                        <div className="obs-error">
                            {error}
                            <button onClick={refresh}>Retry</button>
                        </div>
                    )}
                    <ObservationTable
                        observations={observations}
                        loading={loading}
                        pagination={pagination}
                        onPageChange={(page) => 
                            setFilters(prev => ({...prev, page}))
                        }
                        onView={handleView}
                        onEdit={handleEdit}
                        onDelete={deleteObservation}
                        onStatusChange={updateStatus}
                    />
                </>
            )}

            {activeTab === 'analytics' && (
                <ObservationCharts 
                    stats={stats} 
                    loading={statsLoading} 
                />
            )}

            {/* FORM DRAWER */}
            {showForm && (
                <ObservationForm
                    observation={editingObs}
                    onSubmit={handleFormSubmit}
                    onClose={() => {
                        setShowForm(false);
                        setEditingObs(null);
                    }}
                />
            )}

            {/* DETAIL DRAWER */}
            {viewingObs && (
                <ObservationDetail
                    observation={viewingObs}
                    onClose={() => setViewingObs(null)}
                    onEdit={() => {
                        setEditingObs(viewingObs);
                        setViewingObs(null);
                        setShowForm(true);
                    }}
                />
            )}

        </div>
    );
}

─── CSS: ObservationPage.css ────────────────────────────────

Write all styles using CSS custom properties (tokens).
No hardcoded colors. No !important unless fixing 
existing conflicts.

Key classes to define:

.obs-page {
    padding: 0;
    background: var(--bg-base);
    min-height: 100%;
}

.obs-page__header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-6);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
}

.obs-page__title {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0;
}

.obs-page__subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 4px 0 0;
}

.obs-page__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
}

/* KPI Grid */
.kpi-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: var(--sp-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
}

.kpi-card {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 18px 20px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transition: box-shadow var(--transition-base),
                transform var(--transition-base);
}

.kpi-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.kpi-card__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.kpi-card__icon {
    font-size: 16px;
}

.kpi-card__label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}

.kpi-card__value {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    animation: countUp 0.4s ease-out both;
}

/* Tabs */
.obs-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-subtle);
}

.obs-tab {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    background: none;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    margin-bottom: -2px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color var(--transition-base),
                border-color var(--transition-base);
}

.obs-tab:hover {
    color: var(--text-primary);
}

.obs-tab.active {
    color: var(--green-600);
    border-bottom-color: var(--green-600);
    font-weight: 600;
}

/* Buttons */
.btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 9px 16px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    white-space: nowrap;
}

.btn-primary {
    background: var(--green-600);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xs);
}
.btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--green-700);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
}
.btn-primary:active {
    transform: scale(0.98);
}

.btn-secondary {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
}
.btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--bg-sunken);
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .kpi-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .kpi-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .obs-page__header { flex-direction: column; }
    .obs-page__actions { width: 100%; justify-content: flex-end; }
}
@media (max-width: 480px) {
    .kpi-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .obs-page__title { font-size: var(--text-xl); }
}

/* Table wrapper mobile scroll */
.obs-table-wrapper {
    overflow-x: auto;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
}

/* Drawer overlay */
.drawer-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.42);
    backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
    z-index: 100;
    animation: fadeIn 0.2s ease-out both;
}

.drawer {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    width: 520px;
    max-width: 100vw;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    z-index: 101;
    overflow-y: auto;
    animation: slideInRight 0.26s ease-out both;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
    .drawer { width: 100vw; }
}

